      "content": "but that's the thing, there aren't any meaningful connections. i don't have anyone here. it feels like i'm just taking up space that someone else could actually use. like, there is no impact. if i just... let go, it would be so quiet and peaceful. no one would even have to deal with the mess of me being gone.",
